Key Match Events: Jayson Tatum scored seven of his 29 points in the final seven minutes, going with a pair of assists, a steal and a block.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Celtics rode Jayson Tatum for lengthy stretches, even though Tatum himself was off from 3-point range.
Others: The Celtics won 118-106 over the Nuggets (sans Nikola Jokic) on Tuesday, pulling away in the fourth quarter for a double-digit win.
